          <h3 class="cs-pg-structure-card__title">Doctoral Dissertation</h3>
          <span class="cs-pg-structure-card__credits">Original research (200+ pages)</span>
          <p>A substantial original contribution to knowledge, independently conducted under expert supervision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-pg-structure-card">
          <div class="cs-pg-structure-card__icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
