        </div>
        <div class="cs-pg-req-card">
          <div class="cs-pg-req-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="cs-pg-req-card__title">Research Proposal</h3>
          <p>A clear research proposal or statement of research interests in one of our active research areas.</p>
